#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.68"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.68:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.68:0.2"
msgid "7. Mahāvagga"
msgstr "7. The Great Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.68:0.3"
msgid "68. Aññatitthiyasutta"
msgstr "68. Followers of Other Paths"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:1.1"
msgid "“Sace, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow other paths were to ask:"

msgctxt "an3.68:1.2"
msgid "‘tayome, āvuso, dhammā."
msgstr "‘There are these three things."

msgctxt "an3.68:1.3"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.68:1.4"
msgid "Rāgo, doso, moho—"
msgstr "Greed, hate, delusion."

msgctxt "an3.68:1.5"
msgid "ime kho, āvuso, tayo dhammā."
msgstr "These are the three things."

#. VAR: adhippayāso → adhippāyo (bj) | adhippāyaso (s1-3, km) | adhippāyāso (pts1)
msgctxt "an3.68:1.6"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ, āvuso, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ ko viseso ko adhippayāso kiṃ nānākaraṇan’ti?"
msgstr "What’s the difference between them?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:1.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ kinti "
"byākareyyāthā”ti?"
msgstr "How would you answer them?”"

msgctxt "an3.68:1.8"
msgid ""
"“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā bhagavaṃnettikā bhagavaṃpaṭisaraṇā. Sādhu "
"vata, bhante, bhagavantaṃyeva paṭibhātu etassa bhāsitassa attho. Bhagavato "
"sutvā bhikkhū dhāressantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. He is our guide and our refuge. "
"Sir, may the Buddha himself please clarify the meaning of this. The "
"mendicants will listen and remember it.”"

msgctxt "an3.68:1.9"
msgid "“Tena hi, bhikkhave, suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, mendicants, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "an3.68:1.10"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "an3.68:1.11"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.200"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:2.1"
msgid "“Sace, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow other paths were to ask:"

msgctxt "an3.68:2.2"
msgid "‘tayome, āvuso, dhammā."
msgstr "‘There are these three things."

msgctxt "an3.68:2.3"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.68:2.4"
msgid "Rāgo, doso, moho—"
msgstr "Greed, hate, delusion."

msgctxt "an3.68:2.5"
msgid "ime kho, āvuso, tayo dhammā;"
msgstr "These are the three things."

msgctxt "an3.68:2.6"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ, āvuso, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ ko viseso ko adhippayāso kiṃ nānākaraṇan’ti?"
msgstr "What’s the difference between them?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:2.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ "
"byākareyyātha:"
msgstr "You should answer them:"

msgctxt "an3.68:2.8"
msgid ""
"‘rāgo kho, āvuso, appasāvajjo dandhavirāgī, doso mahāsāvajjo khippavirāgī, "
"moho mahāsāvajjo dandhavirāgī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Greed, reverends, is mildly blameworthy, but slow to fade away. Hate is "
"very blameworthy, but quick to fade away. Delusion is very blameworthy, and "
"slow to fade away.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:3.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ko panāvuso, hetu ko paccayo yena anuppanno vā rāgo uppajjati uppanno vā "
"rāgo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"And if they ask: ‘What is the cause, what is the reason why greed arises, "
"and once arisen it increases and grows?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:3.2"
msgid "‘“Subhanimittan”tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say: ‘The beautiful aspect of things."

msgctxt "an3.68:3.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa subhanimittaṃ ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno vā rāgo uppajjati "
"uppanno vā rāgo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"When you attend improperly on the beautiful aspect of things, greed arises, "
"and once arisen it increases and grows."

msgctxt "an3.68:3.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena anuppanno vā rāgo uppajjati uppanno "
"vā rāgo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why greed arises, and once arisen it "
"increases and grows.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:4.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ko panāvuso, hetu ko paccayo yena anuppanno vā doso uppajjati uppanno vā "
"doso bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"And if they ask: ‘What is the cause, what is the reason why hate arises, and "
"once arisen it increases and grows?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:4.2"
msgid "‘“Paṭighanimittan”tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say: ‘The disagreeable aspect of things."

msgctxt "an3.68:4.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa paṭighanimittaṃ ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno vā doso uppajjati "
"uppanno vā doso bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"When you attend improperly on the disagreeable aspect of things, hate "
"arises, and once arisen it increases and grows."

msgctxt "an3.68:4.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena anuppanno vā doso uppajjati uppanno "
"vā doso bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why hate arises, and once arisen it "
"increases and grows.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:5.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ko panāvuso, hetu ko paccayo yena anuppanno vā moho uppajjati uppanno vā "
"moho bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"And if they ask: ‘What is the cause, what is the reason why delusion arises, "
"and once arisen it increases and grows?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:5.2"
msgid "‘“Ayoniso manasikāro”tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say: ‘Improper attention."

msgctxt "an3.68:5.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno vā moho uppajjati uppanno vā moho "
"bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"When you attend improperly, delusion arises, and once arisen it increases "
"and grows."

msgctxt "an3.68:5.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena anuppanno vā moho uppajjati uppanno "
"vā moho bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why delusion arises, and once arisen "
"it increases and grows.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.201"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: ca → vā (s1-3)
msgctxt "an3.68:6.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ko panāvuso, hetu ko paccayo yena anuppanno ceva rāgo nuppajjati uppanno ca "
"rāgo pahīyatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"And if they ask, ‘What is the cause, what is the reason why greed doesn’t "
"arise, or if it’s already arisen it’s given up?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:6.2"
msgid "‘“Asubhanimittan”tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say: ‘The ugly aspect of things."

msgctxt "an3.68:6.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa asubhanimittaṃ yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva rāgo nuppajjati "
"uppanno ca rāgo pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"When you attend properly on the ugly aspect of things, greed doesn’t arise, "
"or if it’s already arisen it’s given up."

msgctxt "an3.68:6.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena anuppanno ceva rāgo nuppajjati "
"uppanno ca rāgo pahīyatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why greed doesn’t arise, or if it’s "
"already arisen it’s given up.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:7.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ko panāvuso, hetu ko paccayo yena anuppanno ceva doso nuppajjati uppanno ca "
"doso pahīyatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"And if they ask, ‘What is the cause, what is the reason why hate doesn’t "
"arise, or if it’s already arisen it’s given up?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:7.2"
msgid "‘“Mettā cetovimuttī”tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say: ‘The heart’s release by love.’"

msgctxt "an3.68:7.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa mettaṃ cetovimuttiṃ yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva doso "
"nuppajjati uppanno ca doso pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"When you attend properly on the heart’s release by love, hate doesn’t arise, "
"or if it’s already arisen it’s given up."

msgctxt "an3.68:7.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena anuppanno ceva doso nuppajjati "
"uppanno ca doso pahīyatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why hate doesn’t arise, or if it’s "
"already arisen it’s given up.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.68:8.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ko panāvuso, hetu ko paccayo yena anuppanno ceva moho nuppajjati uppanno ca "
"moho pahīyatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"And if they ask, ‘What is the cause, what is the reason why delusion doesn’t "
"arise, or if it’s already arisen it’s given up?’"

msgctxt "an3.68:8.2"
msgid "‘“Yonisomanasikāro”tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say: ‘Proper attention."

msgctxt "an3.68:8.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva moho nuppajjati uppanno ca moho "
"pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"When you attend properly, delusion doesn’t arise, or if it’s already arisen "
"it’s given up."

msgctxt "an3.68:8.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena anuppanno vā moho nuppajjati uppanno "
"ca moho pahīyatī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why delusion doesn’t arise, or if it’s "
"already arisen it’s given up.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.68:8.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
